{"tid":1170827,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"27歲男光顧懷舊英式理髮店　遭兩刀手闖入斬傷","createTime":"2019-05-25T09:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T10:24:48.000Z","uid":6497,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"00104d585f6ee3bd6f5ee0db6bd22be368d6fc57","tid":1170827,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190525/s00001/4011ae14916962c17b4c443f83158bb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190525%2Fs00001%2F4011ae14916962c17b4c443f83158bb1.jpg&h=5d973281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190525/s00001/4011c64fbc3b06e78df58d86e5092f9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190525%2Fs00001%2F4011c64fbc3b06e78df58d86e5092f9f.jpg&h=fe0d509c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n凌晨零時，一名27歲姓陳男子到土瓜灣明倫街1號一間復古的紋身理髮店光顧，於近櫥窗的座椅剪髮期間，兩名戴口罩男子突然闖入向陳男揮刀，他以雙手擋刀受傷，血濺櫥窗及座椅，刀手逞兇後登上接應私家車逃去。<br />\n<br />\n店員大驚報警，陳男雙手受傷清醒送院。警方到場翻看閉路電視片段調查，案件列傷人，交由九龍城警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進。警方正追緝兩名疑犯，其中一人約1.6米高、肥身材、案發時戴口罩、身穿深色上衣；另一人約1.7米高、瘦身材、案發時戴口罩及眼鏡、身穿深色上衣。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，涉事店舖為懷舊英式理髮店加紋身店，由4名鍾情英式文化與復古電單車的店東合資經營，當中2人為髮型師，兩人是紋身師。其中一位店東Mike為電影《春嬌救志明》的專用髮型師，事後他在個人Facebook上報平安。<br />\n<br />\nMike接受電話訪問時表示，陳姓傷者曾光顧十數次，每次均是臨急預約，甫到達店舖便只顧著玩手機，很少與店內職員交流。Mike稱事主曾透露從事金融行業，喜好傳統英式油頭，事發當晚是店內最後一個剪髮客人，其妻坐在店外私家車內等候，Mike為他剪完髮「Gel頭」後，兩名兇徙突然衝入店內向陳男施襲，初時Mike與另外3名職員誤以為有人持棍向陳施襲，後來刀手逃走時看見刀光，再發現陳雙手的刀傷，方知道二人用刀行兇。<br />\n<br />\n「當時同事想上前制止，但對方稱『唔關你事唔好行埋嚟』喝止，他（陳男）被斬後坐在椅上發呆，面容發青雙手傷口見骨。」陳最後由妻子陪同送院。事後Mike與同事一直留在店內清潔消毒，整晚未眠，雖然熟客未有取消預約，又不斷致電關心，但坦言事件會影響街客的信心。"},{"pid":"c0fb377bec4b29ae56672b7b8cabb310016f1799","tid":1170827,"uid":16061,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"從事金融行業"},{"pid":"d50dacaaa23525a98b593eb998878371aedc02a4","tid":1170827,"uid":65887,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://m.daguaw.com/img/aHR0cDovL2ltZzAuaW1ndG4uYmRpbWcuY29tL2l0L3U9MzU1NzgyNTk3MCwyODY4MTM1NTU2JmZtPTI2JmdwPTAuanBn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.daguaw.com%2Fimg%2FaHR0cDovL2ltZzAuaW1ndG4uYmRpbWcuY29tL2l0L3U9MzU1NzgyNTk3MCwyODY4MTM1NTU2JmZtPTI2JmdwPTAuanBn.jpg&h=8389cc3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f506792a99429692459e02b2589db48af885e63","tid":1170827,"uid":69060,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c0fb377bec4b29ae56672b7b8cabb310016f1799","tid":1170827,"uid":16061,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"從事金融行業"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:28:57.000Z","msg":"我哋連登仔話從事金融行業=倫敦金=抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150bc1e095e3009d0a40ebc6d560a9f9a2e052da","tid":1170827,"uid":82532,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:29:13.000Z","msg":"從事金融行業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540aacf4b3ef13042303601ccd36b578faff7cac","tid":1170827,"uid":178317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:30:05.000Z","msg":"整晚未眠都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e148de0e641833d6592c6dc0eb015e001278fef","tid":1170827,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ad09912450b0e6b304a4ef942ee0bb9bc5d5ee","tid":1170827,"uid":70439,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:30:21.000Z","msg":"咁都砍唔死，垃圾刀手"},{"pid":"b6c8f70a29fa3143e4c0ecec31b958b85859f20d","tid":1170827,"uid":39710,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:31:48.000Z","msg":"從事金融行業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你慌